(82, 'Program.Kreativitas.Mahasiswa.PKM.2022', 'informasi', 'Program Kreativitas Mahasiswa (PKM) 2022', '<h3>PENDAFTARAN TIM PKM</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Form Pendaftaran Judul PKM<br /></strong>Daftar Tim / Judul PKM 2022 : <a href=\"https://forms.gle/8vbV3uNTYiWbBcNq8\" target=\"_blank\">di sini<br /><br /></a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Kelompok&nbsp;PKM<br /></strong>Lihat&nbsp;Kelompok / Judul PKM 2022 FKM UNMUL yang sudah di ajukan : <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1arvezFe2mOtS1xw-PEjKeyUWX6-tiTA5AioIrNbYpvk/edit#gid=640768201\" target=\"_blank\">di sini<br /><br /></a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Panduan/Petunjuk Teknis PKM</strong><a href=\"https://forms.gle/8vbV3uNTYiWbBcNq8\" target=\"_blank\"><br /></a>Panduan PKM -&nbsp;Penjelasan Umum :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1sRskAkNNUHrjwZy6nqV6kC1tlAEQoUEE/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">unduh</a><br />1. Panduan PKM - Artikel Ilmiah (AI) : <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ZRGrsW9wcHrjwkyF8ds27kWyhjyMSGta/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">unduh<br /></a>2. Panduan&nbsp;PKM - Gagasan Futuristik Tertulis (GFT) :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/19eIoEW_MVCLOC17WViwEilhAC1agyosN/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">unduh</a><br />3. Panduan PKM - Kewirausahaan (K) : <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1sSQU4q-UqsNiEuy-KdHOR4GY72Bey5x6/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">unduh</a><br />4. Panduan&nbsp;PKM -&nbsp;Karsa Cipta (KC) : <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/17nukxW4cpSkGg4AyzymVYSh8JQl2z45r/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">unduh<br /></a>5.&nbsp;Panduan&nbsp;PKM - Karya Inovatif (KI) :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1y_vqsL5p7gwAsAYK2rwgY3bRbQT8p0At/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">unduh</a><br />6. Panduan&nbsp;PKM -&nbsp;Penerapan Iptek (PI) : <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Wj0IZERv_u2EgO8ABZOBn_6-x7yKhHVK/view?usp=sharing\" target=\"_blank\">unduh</a><br />7. Panduan&nbsp;PKM -&nbsp;Pengabdian Kepada Masyarakat (