ouid=116202017401542790901&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\" target=\"_blank\">Unduh</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Kuesioner Safety Induction FKM Unmul</h3>\r\n<p>Pre test Safety Induction : <a href=\"https://bit.ly/Pretestsafetyinduction\" target=\"_blank\">Unduh</a></p>\r\n<p>Post test Safety Induction : <a href=\"https://bit.ly/Posttestsafetyinductionunmul\" target=\"_blank\">Unduh</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Video Safety Induction Gedung Baru FKM Unmul</h3>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/F0EDIp68M0E\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>Video&nbsp;Pengenalan FKM Unmul</h3>\r\n<p><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/ypjFThzxXHs\" width=\"560\" height=\"314\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2022-08-24 10:08:55', 'safety induction', 'admin', 13),
(88, 'International.Conference.Public.Health', 'informasi', 'International Conference Public Health', '<h3><img src=\"../../../../public/upload/galeri/369372284899b8894f065a52bb02438c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"722\" height=\"120\" /><br /><img src=\"../../../../public/upload/galeri/e7abcc548227b748bc60e5e27ca1839c.JPG\" width=\"721\" height=\"1076\" /></h3>\r\n<h4><strong>Announcement of Abstract and Poster Accepted on The 1st MICTOPH</strong></h4>\r\n<p>Here we attach the announcement of the abstract and poster accepted after going through the review process.</p>\r\n<p>We congratulate those who are accepted and thank you very much for all the participation of the registrants. See you on November 12th!</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1l1cmvM3WtMs2hPZk6blupH71Ixspwag8/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Title</strong></h4>\r\n<p>&ldquo;The First Mulawarman International Conference on Tropical Public Health&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Theme</strong></h4>\r\n<p>&ldquo;Digital Health for Public Health on Post-Pandemic Covid-19&rdquo;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>Time and The place Implementation</strong></h4>\r\n<p>This conference will be held on:</p>\r\n<p>Day, date : <strong>Saturday , November 12, 2022</strong></p>\r\n<p>The place : <strong>Online via zoom meeting</strong> (based on the Faculty Public Health , University Mulawarman , Samarinda , Indonesia)</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h4><strong>SPEAKER</strong></h4>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../../../public/upload/galeri/659281f0dfb8ba2275996368a6649aa1.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"152\" /><strong><br /></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../../public/upload/galeri/5a44b299b5441b17940a73a956a1a3fb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"718\" height=\"404\" /></strong></p>\r\n<h4><strong>REGISTRATION</strong></h4>\r\n<p><strong>Participant</strong></p>\r\n<p>The target participants for this international conference are students (S1, S2, S3), alumnus, and professionals in the fields of health and education (target participants: 300 people). Participants will get certificates for both attending as presenters and participants after participating in conference activities.</p>\r\n<p>oral presenters and seminar participants will get certificates with SKP (employee performance goals) of professional organizations (IAKMI and PERSAKMI).</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Registration </strong></p>\r\n<p>Participants can register themselves as presenters (oral or poster) and webinar participants via link : <strong><a href=\"https://bit.ly/RegistrationMICTOPH2022\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/RegistrationMICTOPH2022</a></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Payment Virtual Account&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Payment Virtual Account : 9880460200100018</p>\r\n<p>Name : The 1st MICTOPH</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Registration Fee</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Registration fee for oral presenter (include seminar participation fee):</strong> <br />- General : IDR 500.000<br />- Doctoral student : IDR 350.000<br />- Master student : IDR 250.000<br />- Bachelor student : IDR 100.000<br />#International Presenter: USD 35</p>\r\n<p><strong>Registration Fee for Poster (include seminar participation fee):</strong></p>\r\n<p>- General IDR 350.000<br />- Doctoral IDR 200.000<br />- Master IDR 150.000<br />- Bachelor IDR 75.000<br />- International USD 20</p>\r\n<p><strong>Seminar participant fee:</strong><br />- From FKM UNMUL: free<br />- Outside FKM UNMUL : IDR 50.000<br />#International Participant (non presenter) : USD 7</p>\r\n<p><strong>Publication Fee:</strong> <br />Scopus or Web of Science index proceedings will be informed later.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Contact Person:</strong></p>\r\n<p>+6281355916627 (Nurul)<br />+6287865692030 (Rina)</p>\r\n<p>E-mail:<br />mictoph@fkm.unmul.ac.id</p>\r\n<p><strong>Call for Paper</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Topic :</strong> Digital Health for Public Health on Post-Pandemic Covid-19 (based on the 8 pillars of public health)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Sub- topics :</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Biostatistics and Population</li>\r\n<li>Environmental Health</li>\r\n<li>Health Promotion</li>\r\n<li>Nutrition</li>\r\n<li>Occupational Health and Safety</li>\r\n<li>Health Administration and Policy</li>\r\n<li>Epidemiology</li>\r\n<li>Child and Maternal Health</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Provision Writing Abstract </strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Title should not exceed 15 words</li>\r\n<li>Abstract manuscript consisting of one page with a maximum of 250 words, which is made in English</li>\r\n<li>Abstract contains background, objectives, research methods, results, suggestions, and keywords</li>\r\n<li>If non-research / community service results, the abstract can contain: background, objectives, implementation methods, results (activity stages, review results, etc.), lessons learned, and keywords.</li>\r\n<li>Abstract writing using Times New Roman font, size 12 pts and spacing 1</li>\r\n<li>Abstracts are sent in Microsoft Word format.</li>\r\n<li>Abstract sent via link : <a href=\"https://bit.ly/RegistrationMICTOPH2022\">Upload Your Abstract</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Provision Presentation Video Delivery</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Videos collected after the selection process of abstract announced and participant received a Letter of Acceptance ( LoA )</li>\r\n<li>Video showing presenter and presentation slides</li>\r\n<li>Video duration max 7 minutes</li>\r\n<li>Maximum video capacity 100 mb</li>\r\n<li>Videos collected on the link <a href=\"https://forms.gle/m5X7KFWEpT4dZLUr7\">Upload Your Video</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Provision Script Complete Article (Full Paper)</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Full text of a maximum of 4000 words</li>\r\n<li>Complete manuscript structure:\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\">\r\n<li>Title</li>\r\n<li>Abstract and keywords</li>\r\n<li>Introduction</li>\r\n<li>Purpose</li>\r\n<li>Research method / implementation Method</li>\r\n<li>Results and Discussion</li>\r\n<li>Suggestions / lessons learned</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Maximum Full Paper capacity 10&nbsp;mb</li>\r\n<li>Articles are collected on the link <a href=\"https://forms.gle/m5X7KFWEpT4dZLUr7\">Upload Your Abstract</a></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><strong>Provision Poster Complete (Poster Presentation)</strong></p>\r\n<p>1. Customize the content of the poster with the template</p>\r\n<p>2. Please complete the poster with pictures and/or diagrams</p>\r\n<p>3. Upload the complete poster at the following link&nbsp;<a href=\"https://forms.gle/VHU5As61jGjJEoV16\">Upload Your&nbsp;Poster<br /><br /></a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Article Publication</strong></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Prior to the conference, participants will be given a book of abstract</li>\r\n<li>After the conference activities and complete articles have been collected, the selected articles will be published in the Web of Science or Scopus indexed proceedings.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Poster&nbsp;Template&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Download&nbsp;Poster&nbsp;Template&nbsp; here :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1tyd1b09U2AzAbooc1JWi6KZdQp43QVU2/edit?usp=sharing&amp;ouid=100104818473757789352&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Abstract Template&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Download Abstract Template&nbsp; here :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/10bMiQHo3FOn7fGOqGXHGJaRe14bgqX8U/edit?usp=sharing&amp;ouid=100104818473757789352&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Full Paper Template&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>Download Full Paper Template&nbsp; here :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/14DnGtMQvpLAWAdZBvK4STgTfxiMDqkWG/edit?usp=share_link&amp;ouid=107937252377523467476&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Term of Reference</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><img src=\"../../../../public/upload/galeri/1f84c097a8f075eaca70e3757356e9a7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"456\" height=\"1054\" /></strong></p>\r\n<p>Download Term of Reference&nbsp;here :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rOs1DB6yzi6AMBnY6uiLRqdzfooCxXnf/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></p>\r\n<p><strong>Co-Host</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../../../public/upload/galeri/2f87943bd2ea4fe455483360ef4e550c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"101\" height=\"102\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"../../../../public/upload/galeri/0e6a2e03c942419b6ecc41b6e2798cea.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"108\" height=\"108\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"../../../../public/upload/galeri/7c4e3a9b611a9a0c71af106a80f3d65c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"103\" height=\"105\" /></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"../../../../public/upload/galeri/085bce8266daa1c68d4f329269424727.jpg\" width=\"724\" height=\"98\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '2022-11-02 06:39:07', 'seminar internasional', 'admin', 5),
